ProtoResult:
. "If $R$ is a complete set of residues modulo $n$ and 
   $a\in\mathbf{Z}$ with $\gcd(a,n)=1$, then $aR = \{ax : x \in
   R\}$ is also a complete set of residues modulo $n$."
